<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Garo Farewell 2026</title>

<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #000000, #1a1a1a);
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
    }

    header {
        padding: 50px 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #d4af37, #000);
    }

    header h1 {
        font-size: 3em;
        margin: 0;
    }

    header p {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        margin-top: 10px;
    }

    section {
        padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    h2 {
        color: #d4af37;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .gallery img {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        object-fit: cover;
        margin: 10px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .gallery img:hover {
        transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    .card {
        background: #222;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 10px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        display: inline-block;
        width: 250px;
    }

    footer {
        padding: 20px;
        background: black;
        color: gray;
    }

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>🎓 Garo Farewell 2026</h1>
    <p>Memories that will stay forever 💛</p>
</header>

<section>
    <h2>📅 Event Details</h2>
    <p><b>Date:</b> 1 May 2026 </p>
    <p><b>Venue:</b> Hotel Neexotica, Banquet Hall Azara, Opp.Mountain Shadow, Guwahati, 781017</p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>📸 Gallery</h2>
    <div class="gallery">
        <img src="photo1.jpg">
        <img src="photo2.jpg">
        <img src="photo3.jpg">
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>💬 Messages</h2>
    <div class="card">"Best memories with you all ❤️"</div>
    <div class="card">"We’ll miss these days forever ✨"</div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>🎶 Music</h2>
    <audio controls autoplay loop>
        <source src="song.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
    </audio>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>Made with ❤️ for Garo Farewell 2026</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
